fields.title: Welcome To
fields.description: As an architect in Welcome To..., you want to build the best new town in the United States of the 1950s by adding resources to a pool, hiring employees, and more.

fields.title: Settlers of Catan
fields.description: Collect and trade resources to build up the island of Catan in this modern classic.

fields.title: Dungeons & Dragons
fields.description: Dungeons & Dragons (commonly abbreviated as D&D or DnD) is a fantasy tabletop role-playing game (RPG) originally designed by Gary Gygax and Dave Arneson.
